---
title: Shrimp & Scallop Scampi with Parsley & Parmesan
description: Get ready to impress your dinner companions with this homemade version of an Italian restaurant favorite. Shrimp and scallops are sautéed until tender, then tossed with al dente spaghetti. Of course, it wouldn’t be a scampi without plenty of cheese and butter—here, you’ll use garlic herb butter as the base for an easy, yet wow-worthy, sauce with Parmesan, parsley, and lemon juice. Add a sprinkle of chili flakes for heat, then all that’s left to do is pour the vino. Buon appetito!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/61f985d8a687c94f6022b36a-01a4b37c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/shrimp-scallop-scampi-61f985d8a687c94f6022b36a-67f86cee.pdf
servings: 2
author: Sara Heilman
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/shrimp-and-scallop-scampi-61f985d8a687c94f6022b36a
time required: 30 minutes
course: main course
cuisine: Italian
